  <h2><a href="library/chinafaqs/chinas-energy-conservation-accomplishments-11th-five-year-plan" title="ChinaFAQs: China’s Energy Conservation Accomplishments of the 11th Five Year Plan">ChinaFAQs: China’s Energy Conservation Accomplishments of the 11th Five Year Plan</a></h2>

      <span class="submitted">Posted by ChinaFAQs on Jul 25, 2011</span>
  
  <div class="content clear-block">
    <div class="field field-type-filefield field-field-image">
    <div class="field-items">
            <div class="field-item odd">
                    <a href="library/chinafaqs/chinas-energy-conservation-accomplishments-11th-five-year-plan" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-linked imagecache-news-image_linked"><img src="files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/ChinaFAQs_11th_5-Year_Plan_Energy_Conservation_v1_0.jpg" alt="" title="" width="93" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image"/></a>        </div>
        </div>
</div>
<div class="field field-type-filefield field-field-library-file">
      <div class="field-label">Library File:&nbsp;</div>
    <div class="field-items">
            <div class="field-item odd">
                    <div class="filefield-file"><img class="filefield-icon field-icon-application-pdf"  alt="application/pdf icon" src="sites/all/modules/filefield/icons/application-pdf.png" /><a href="files/chinainfo/ChinaFAQs_11th_5-Year_Plan_Energy_Conservation_0.pdf" type="application/pdf; length=294188">ChinaFAQs_11th_5-Year_Plan_Energy_Conservation.pdf</a></div>        </div>
        </div>
</div>
<p><b>Key Points</b></p>

<blockquote><blockquote>
<ul>
<li>China’s mounting energy demand spurred by rapid economic growth prompted important energy-saving measures in its 11th Five Year Plan.  

</li><li>Researchers found that many projects conceived to improve energy intensity were on track to meet or surpass their goals, while others have lagged.

</li><li>The study offers recommendations for strengthening future efforts.
</li></ul>
</blockquote></blockquote>
  </div>
<div class="clear-block">
    	<div class="readmore"> <a href="library/chinafaqs/chinas-energy-conservation-accomplishments-11th-five-year-plan">Read more</a> </div>
  </div>

